{"tid":1708334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正名行動]由今日起改口稱制止暴徒既行為做\"執法\"","createTime":"2019-11-11T14:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T01:26:20.000Z","uid":34816,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99f9544096bf5d1019224d805b7b0e128ba970c6","tid":1708334,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"係今時今日，班所謂既香港警察目無法紀濫權濫暴、選擇執法既時候，佢地已經唔配叫做執法者，佢地只係淪為呢個港共獨裁政權既走狗，只係為左打壓市民而存在。<br />\n<br />\n我地而家做既只係掌握翻屬於人民既公權力，致力保護自己既城市同他人財產安全，當下次再遇到有暴徒襲擊而自衛既時候，唔好再講私了，應該改口做<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">執法，</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地每一個香港市民都係執法者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1ff2a6c2785df958cdac750183e6c893e94f69c8","tid":1708334,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"「黎明行動」低風險新職業 - 搬屋師/升降師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1704038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1704038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5fb2465312ac9c0ea60049842d5e0c4a61afdbe4","tid":1708334,"uid":34816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"聽日開始我希望見到各頻道係寫XX位置有市民執法中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c8cdb3844a71b565118d468a70f05bdeeb24d6","tid":1708334,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9c19911e3b3b999264d805ac589e005af47303","tid":1708334,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse